name: Vessels 141: GARR THE BEAST SLAYER
description:
To catch a beast, you have to think like a beast, that is Garr the Beast Slayer’s motto. And to think like a beast, you don’t necessarily have to DRESS like a beast, but who wouldn’t want to dress like a beast? Especially one with a gleaming, rock hard carapace and sensually curved horns and an alluring, lobster-red hue? That is Garr the Beast Slayer’s OTHER motto.

He doesn’t share that one with as many people as the first motto.
